===Etymology===
From {{etyl|fro|en}} {{term|descreistre|lang=fro}} (French: {{term|décroître|lang=fr}}), from {{etyl|la|en}} {{term|decrescere|lang=la}}.

===Verb===
{{en-verb|decreas|ing}}

# {{context|intransitive|lang=en}} Of a quantity, to become [[smaller]].
# {{context|transitive|lang=en}} To make (a quantity) smaller.

====Synonyms====
